summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing improvements to certain streets adjacent to and in the vicinity of the South Seattle Urban Renewal Redevelopment Project; reimbursing the Department of Community Development for landscaping work in City property outside said Project area; making a partially reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor; and abandoning unencumbered balances in appropriations in connection therewith made by Ordinance 96889.
